---
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';
---

<Base title="工具箱 — 雕龙 DragonCraft" locale="zh">
  <div class="page-header">
    <h1>工具箱</h1>
    <p>让叙事能力可衡量、可练习</p>
  </div>

  <div class="page-content">
    <div class="tools-grid">

      <div class="tool-card tool-featured">
        <span class="tool-num">01</span>
        <span class="tool-cat">测试</span>
        <h3>叙事人格测试</h3>
        <p>发现你的叙事风格类型：INTJ战略型 / ENFJ激励型 / ENFP创意型 / INFJ隐喻型</p>
        <div class="tool-meta">
          <span class="tool-meta-item">🧭 8道题</span>
          <span class="tool-meta-item">⏱️ 3分钟</span>
        </div>
        <a href="https://github.com/lj22503/diaolong-skill/blob/main/tools/叙事人格测试-图文版.md" target="_blank" class="tool-btn">开始测试 →</a>
      </div>

      <div class="tool-card">
        <span class="tool-num">02</span>
        <span class="tool-cat">评估</span>
        <h3>八刀评估表</h3>
        <p>从历史、辩证、现象、语言、形式、存在、美感、元反思八个维度评估叙事质量。</p>
        <a href="https://github.com/lj22503/diaolong-skill/blob/main/tools/八刀评估提示词.md" target="_blank" class="tool-btn-outline">查看评估表 →</a>
      </div>

      <div class="tool-card">
        <span class="tool-num">03</span>
        <span class="tool-cat">模板</span>
        <h3>15+ 场景模板</h3>
        <p>个人IP、品牌故事、产品发布、融资Pitch、销售脚本……拿来即用。</p>
        <a href="https://github.com/lj22503/diaolong-skill/tree/main/templates" target="_blank" class="tool-btn-outline">查看模板 →</a>
      </div>

    </div>
  </div>
</Base>

<style>
  .tools-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fill, minmax(280px, 1fr));
    gap: 20px;
  }
  .tool-card {
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: var(--radius);
    padding: 28px;
    background: white;
    position: relative;
    transition: box-shadow 0.2s, transform 0.2s;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 12px;
  }
  .tool-card:hover {
    box-shadow: 0 4px 16px rgba(0,0,0,0.08);
    transform: translateY(-2px);
  }
  .tool-featured {
    border-color: var(--accent);
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(192,57,43,0.03) 0%, white 100%);
  }
  .tool-num {
    font-family: var(--font-serif);
    font-size: 2.5rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--border);
    position: absolute;
    top: 20px;
    right: 24px;
  }
  .tool-cat {
    display: inline-block;
    font-size: 0.72rem;
    color: var(--accent);
    background: rgba(192,57,43,0.08);
    padding: 2px 8px;
    border-radius: 3px;
    width: fit-content;
  }
  .tool-card h3 { font-size: 1rem; font-weight: 600; margin: 0; }
  .tool-card p { color: var(--text-muted); font-size: 0.88rem; line-height: 1.7; margin: 0; }
  .tool-meta {
    display: flex;
    gap: 12px;
    margin-top: 4px;
  }
  .tool-meta-item {
    font-size: 0.78rem;
    color: var(--text-muted);
  }
  .tool-btn {
    display: inline-block;
    background: var(--accent);
    color: white;
    padding: 8px 18px;
    border-radius: 5px;
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    font-weight: 500;
    text-decoration: none;
    margin-top: auto;
    transition: background 0.15s;
    width: fit-content;
  }
  .tool-btn:hover { background: var(--accent-hover); color: white; }
  .tool-btn-outline {
    display: inline-block;
    border: 1px solid var(--accent);
    color: var(--accent);
    padding: 8px 18px;
    border-radius: 5px;
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    font-weight: 500;
    text-decoration: none;
    margin-top: auto;
    width: fit-content;
    transition: all 0.15s;
  }
  .tool-btn-outline:hover { background: var(--accent); color: white; }
</style>
